  "prompt": "Which is your favorite hangout place in Pune?",
  "response": "I don\u2019t have personal experiences or preferences, but I can suggest popular hangout places in Pune! Some favorites among locals and visitors include:\n\n1. **Koregaon Park** \u2013 Known for its vibrant cafes and restaurants.\n2. **FC Road** \u2013 A bustling area with food stalls, cafes, and shops.\n3. **Viman Nagar** \u2013 Offers a mix of shopping and dining experiences.\n4. **Panchgani & Lonavala** \u2013 Popular hill stations near Pune for a weekend getaway.\n5. **Shaniwar Wada** \u2013 A historical fort that\u2019s great for a day visit.\n\nEach spot has its unique charm, so it depends on what kind of atmosphere you\u2019re looking for!",
